# --- NOTE: data/ and index/ are intentionally NOT ignored ---
# The scraped commits/PRs/issues (data/*.json) and the built FAISS index
# (index/) are committed on purpose, so a fresh clone or deployment has a
# working system immediately without re-scraping GitHub or rebuilding the
# index from scratch.
